column5: One nothing against Germany is not good enough. What will they do when they face a team (Russia) that shoots back? They are trying to be way too pretty. And I hate the bloody cycle. Jim
Alright, it's looking a bit better now. Jim
4 - 1 they're looking good!!! and yeah that shot from the point by Wieber WOW   First time seeing a puck going throught the net
